Package appeng.api.inventories

Interface IDynamicPartBakedModel

All Superinterfaces:
net.minecraft.client.resources.model.BakedModel
public interface IDynamicPartBakedModel extends net.minecraft.client.resources.model.BakedModel
This interface can be implemented by baked models returned by IPart.getStaticModels() to indicate that they would like to use the model data returned by IPart.getRenderAttachmentData().
